"Adversity": "Losing your semester's data to a corrupted drive is adversity, a circumstance with institutional remedies, not a referendum on your future in science.",
"Recovery": "Recovery after a failed lab exam is one corrected technique and one completed week, the same modest definition you would accept for any system returning to range.",
